 7:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>In health care today, we spend most of the dollars --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426000' id='t-426000'>in terms of treating disease --</span>
