</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='456000' id='t-456000'>So, this is the website of the National Cancer Institute.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459000' id='t-459000'>And I'm here to tell you, it's wrong.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462000' id='t-462000'>So, the website of the National Cancer Institute</span>
