<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='508000' id='t-508000'>The goal of me as a cancer doctor is not to understand cancer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>And I think that's been the fundamental problem over the last five decades,</span>
