</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>I got up at the American Association of Cancer Research,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='528000' id='t-528000'>one of the big cancer research meetings, with 20,000 people there,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532000' id='t-532000'>and I said, &quot;We've made a mistake.</span>
