<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587000' id='t-587000'>The key is, when you look at these variables and you look at this data,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591000' id='t-591000'>you have to understand the data inputs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>You know, if I measured your temperature over 30 days,</span>
