<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>And so, if you think of cancer as a system,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>there's an input and an output and a state in the middle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>So, the states, are equivalent classes of history,</span>
