<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>And so, the problem is that it's not just one system,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699000' id='t-699000'>it's multiple systems on multiple scales.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>It's a system of systems.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>And so, when you start to look at emergent systems,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707000' id='t-707000'>you can look at a neuron under a microscope.</span>
