<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='800000' id='t-800000'>Nobody has ever shown -- and this will be shocking --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803000' id='t-803000'>nobody has ever shown that most chemotherapy</span>
